<verse eid="1SA 31:12"/><verse number="13" style="v" sid="1SA 31:13"/><char style="w" closed="true" strong="H3947">וַיִּקְחוּ֙</char> <char style="w" closed="true" strong="H0853">אֶת</char>־<char style="w" closed="true" strong="H6106">עַצְמֹ֣תֵיהֶ֔ם </char> <char style="w" closed="true" strong="H6912">וַיִּקְבְּר֥וּ</char> <char style="w" closed="true" strong="H8478">תַֽחַת</char>־<char style="w" closed="true" strong="H0815">הָאֶ֖שֶׁל </char> <char style="w" closed="true" strong="H3003">בְּיָבֵ֑שָׁה</char> <char style="w" closed="true" strong="H6684">וַיָּצֻ֖מוּ</char> <char style="w" closed="true" strong="H7651">שִׁבְעַ֥ת</char> <char style="w" closed="true" strong="H3117">יָמִֽים</char>׃ פ   <verse eid="1SA 31:13"/></para>
